ProofArchived CD_add_proj0: forall z w, CD_carr z -> CD_carr w -> proj0 (z :+: w) = proj0 z + proj0 w.

ProofArchived CD_add_proj1: forall z w, CD_carr z -> CD_carr w -> proj1 (z :+: w) = proj1 z + proj1 w.

